Below are the preparation resources that I've used 

Official K8s documentation : https://kubernetes.io/docs/home/ (Allowed in the actual exam as well)
Practice : https://github.com/dgkanatsios/CKAD-exercises (Must practice is these exercises as these are helpful to get deeper understanding on all the concepts)
CKAD Udemy course by Mumshad - https://www.udemy.com/share/1013BQ/
KillerCoda : https://killercoda.com/killer-shell-ckad
Attemp killer.sh after the preparation to get used to the exam environment.
